        "char_start": 433,
        "episode_id": "ep-febd9a8f53bf3a3a",
        "speaker_id": "person:speaker-01",
        "text": "I'll just say it \u2014 I genuinely love Peak Design. Not sponsored, not paid, I just think they're doing the right thing for field kit.",
